# Liolaemus wari

| genus = Liolaemus
| species = wari
| authority = Aguilar, Wood, Cusi, Guzman, Huari, Lundberg, Mortensen, Ramirez, Robles, Suarez, Ticona, Vargas, Venegas, & Sites, 2013
}}
Liolaemus wari is a species of lizard in the family Iguanidae or the family Liolaemidae. The species is endemic to Peru.
